source.name: Claiborne Corridor Study
source.description: New Orleans has been awarded a $2 million federal grant to study ways to revitalize the Claiborne Avenue corridor, included in the .zip file are polygon shapefiles for: 'Claiborne Corridor Linear Extent', 'Claiborne Corridor Areal Extent', and 'Choice Neighborhood Initiative' (http://www.ibervilletreme.org/), and 'Claiborne Corridor Public Housing'.  Last update 11/09/2012
